Ayomide Temilade Oluwatoyosi Folorunso (amụrụ n'abalị iri na asaa n'ọnwa Ọktoba n'afọ 1996) bụ onye Ịtali na-eme egwuregwu ịgba ọsọ na-ahụ maka ihe mgbochi mita 400. O sonyere na 4 × 400 mita relay na 2015 World Championships na Beijing.
Ezinụlọ ya sitere na Naijiria, mana kemgbe afọ 2004 Ayomide na nne na nna ya Ebola, nne ya Mariam na nna ya Emmanuel, onye na-ahụ maka igwu ala, biri na Fidenza

O yighị azzurro na 2013 World Youth Championships in Athletics n'agbanyeghị na ọ nwetara opekata mpe na nka ise, n'ihi na ọ natara paspọtụ Ịtali ya ụbọchị ole na ole mgbe asọmpi ụwa gasịrị, ya mere ọ bụ onye otu egwuregwu mba Ịtali.
